635
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:06,640
I think

636
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:08,039
your current state

637
00:30:08,039 --> 00:30:09,920
is perfect for joining our law firm.

638
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:11,640
I've mentioned it before,

639
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:12,640
but I feel

640
