I must insist again today.

641
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,319
Li.

642
00:30:16,559 --> 00:30:17,984
People have their own aspirations.

643
00:30:18,759 --> 00:30:20,519
Let's not repeat

644
00:30:20,880 --> 00:30:22,160
