645
00:30:22,799 --> 00:30:23,599
Yes.

646
00:30:23,599 --> 00:30:26,400
You were the best students in your year.

647
00:30:27,079 --> 00:30:28,359
No matter where you are,

648
00:30:28,799 --> 00:30:30,440
you can achieve results.

649
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,880
If Lin stays in the prosecution office,

650
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:35,200
