656
00:30:52,759 --> 00:30:54,640
I have lived more than half of my life.

657
00:30:55,279 --> 00:30:56,839
I need to tell you the truth.

658
00:30:58,759 --> 00:31:00,880
Regardless of
whether you are a prosecutor or not,

659
00:31:01,319 --> 00:31:04,440
you should be pragmatic.

660
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:06,960
For Wan Xuemin's case

661
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:08,880
you're working on,

662
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:09,960
we

663
00:31:11,559 --> 00:31:12,599
can still

664
