discuss it.

665
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:16,279
I understand, Mr. Xiao.

666
00:31:18,359 --> 00:31:19,279
No matter what,

667
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:21,319
I'm grateful

668
00:31:21,319 --> 00:31:22,400
