675
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:38,200
Right or wrong,

676
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:39,240
it's my choice.

677
00:31:40,599 --> 00:31:41,839
This cup of tea

678
00:31:41,839 --> 00:31:43,039
means nothing.

679
00:31:43,759 --> 00:31:44,920
Wish you good health.

680
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:54,119
Go ahead to eat.

681
00:31:54,119 --> 00:31:55,000
I'm leaving now.

682
00:31:55,559 --> 00:31:57,279
