683
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,319
Mr. Xiao is still inside.

684
00:32:03,359 --> 00:32:04,119
Li Daoran.

685
00:32:04,559 --> 00:32:07,000
Do you know a person's appearance
follows their heart?

686
00:32:07,759 --> 00:32:09,240
Do you know what you look like now?

687
00:32:15,828 --> 00:32:17,984
(Yang's Diner)

688
00:32:18,359 --> 00:32:19,480
Prosecutor Zheng.

689
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:21,200
You're mysterious.

690
00:32:22,680 --> 00:32:23,480
Why left

691
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:25,319
