692
00:32:25,319 --> 00:32:26,640
Afraid I'll protest

693
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:28,200
or Bai Enyu will?

694
00:32:31,599 --> 00:32:33,240
I'm afraid if I see you,

695
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,480
I won't want to leave.

696
00:32:36,039 --> 00:32:37,440
And you said

697
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:38,799
about trees and seeds.

698
00:32:39,359 --> 00:32:41,440
Prosecutor Fu probably struggled
carrying that.

699
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:43,039
He probably didn't know what it meant.

700
00:32:43,599 --> 00:32:45,119
I was reminding him

701
00:32:45,119 --> 00:32:46,559
to be more responsible.

702
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:49,960
Let me interview our former prosecutor.

703
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:52,839
How does it feel to work in a new field?

704
00:32:54,559 --> 00:32:56,400
You're so petty!

705
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:57,000
Yes.

706
00:33:01,599 --> 00:33:04,160
After I go to the Women's Federation,

707
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:05,759
I plan to focus more

708
00:33:05,759 --> 00:33:07,119
on anti-domestic violence

709
00:33:07,119 --> 00:33:08,079
and child protection.

710
00:33:08,079 --> 00:33:10,039
In the future, we will be sister units.

711
00:33:10,039 --> 00:33:11,319
We can tackle issues together.

712
00:33:11,519 --> 00:33:12,039
Okay.

713
00:33:12,039 --> 00:33:13,599
Do you have

714
00:33:13,856 --> 00:33:14,519
any

715
00:33:14,519 --> 00:33:16,440
open positions for Bai Enyu?

716
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,720
Let me think.

717
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:21,960
Maybe I can ask
the Communist Youth League

718
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:24,240
or the Social Aid Bureau.

719
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:25,119
Really considering it?

720
00:33:25,119 --> 00:33:26,079
I was joking.

721
00:33:26,079 --> 00:33:28,880
He's still of some use
in juvenile prosecution.

722
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:30,240
Let's eat and talk.

723
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,160
Eat.

724
00:33:31,599 --> 00:33:32,640
Now,

725
00:33:32,864 --> 00:33:33,920
your ambition's changed.

726
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:35,000
Don't want

727
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:37,119
