728
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:38,720
No, still the same.

729
00:33:39,319 --> 00:33:41,480
You just mentioned
multi-department coordination.

730
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:42,279
It can establish

731
00:33:42,279 --> 00:33:43,720
