732
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:45,440
That's even harder.

733
00:33:45,839 --> 00:33:47,079
I'm fit for the hardest jobs.

734
00:33:49,599 --> 00:33:51,480
Juvenile prosecution is essentially

735
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:53,720
one tree

736
00:33:54,079 --> 00:33:55,440
shaking another tree,

737
00:33:55,599 --> 00:33:56,599
a cloud

738
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:58,319
pushing another cloud,

739
00:33:58,799 --> 00:34:00,799
and a soul awakening another soul.

740
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:03,720
Should I write this down?

741
00:34:04,559 --> 00:34:05,359
Remember it.

742
00:34:05,519 --> 00:34:06,640
I'll memorize it.

743
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:07,440
Do it now.

744
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,000
Tomorrow.

745
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,568
I'll call you tomorrow and recite it.

746
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:12,320
That quote's from an educator.

747
00:34:13,039 --> 00:34:15,360
Using one pen to guard another.

748
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:17,119
For you.

749
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:19,920
This is for me?

750
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:24,039
Let's call it a legacy.

751
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:27,239
